{"tid":2070333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廈門教會被屈「反黨」遭破壞","createTime":"2020-06-19T05:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T05:16:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e7e90a232e01d19177b30326cf4f211236e19b","tid":2070333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:16:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200619/46I7U5ZSSY3K5G3EHZLUEMKRDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200619%2F46I7U5ZSSY3K5G3EHZLUEMKRDM%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=89b7f886\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200619%2F46I7U5ZSSY3K5G3EHZLUEMKRDM%2F&h=6b748400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200619/46I7U5ZSSY3K5G3EHZLUEMKRDM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n廈門教會被屈「反黨」遭破壞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LIJ7GYOTBIEMAPIVPKIMNU3ECM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLIJ7GYOTBIEMAPIVPKIMNU3ECM.gif&h=d0d2218b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廈門杏光教會樓下有執法人員駐守。 <br />\n<br />\n中共再度打壓內地家庭教會，專門報道內地宗教及人權消息的網媒《寒冬》（Bitter Winter）報道，福建廈門基督教家庭教會「杏光教會」頻遭當局打壓，教會自辦學堂也被認為「反黨」而遭到取締。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牧師︰政府黑社會化<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，以私人住宅作為聚會地點的杏光教會，本月11日上午被數百名公安及城管強行闖入並破壞，。。。。。。。。。。。。，廈門政府已經黑社會化了&hellip;&hellip;這也是這幾年來中國黑社會化的一個縮影。」<br />\n<br />\n今次是杏光教會繼5月3日遭暴力衝擊後，第二次被打擊。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，多人被打傷，六名信徒被警方扣查12小時。<br />\n<br />\n一名教友表示，被衝擊後，教會門口每日都有警察從早到晚12小時站崗、巡查，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，在教會裏長大的孩子容易勾結境外勢力，反對國家、反對黨。<br />\n<br />\n《寒冬》網站"},{"pid":"e873857715be840128d744af4ca5794c9b11067c","tid":2070333,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"幾時到佛教(印度)"}]}